武汉同济医院一线医生口述：每天面对死亡，紧张但不恐惧——专访武汉同济医院心内科医生赵金召。
Wuhan Tongji Hospital first-line doctor oral: daily face of death, tension but not fear - Interview Wuhan Tongji Hospital heart physician Zhao Jinchuan.
张晓晖2020-01-31 15:53。
Zhang Xiaohui 2020-01-31 15: 53.
扫描二维码分享到朋友圈。
Scanning two-dimensional code to share with friends.
经济观察网 记者 张晓晖 在这次始自武汉、蔓延至全国的新型冠状病毒肺炎疫情中，华中科技大学同济医学院附属同济医院（以下简称“武汉同济医院”）是武汉最早收治非冠病患的几家医院之一。
Zhang Xiaohui, a reporter from the Economic Observation Network, was one of the first hospitals in Wuhan to treat patients with non-crowning coronavirus pneumonia, a new type of coronavirus pneumonia that spread from Wuhan to the whole country.
。
.
武汉同济医院历史悠久，其1900年由同济医院由德国医师埃里希·宝隆在上海创办，1955年迁至武汉，至今拥有120年的历史。
Wuhan Tongji Hospital, founded in 1900 in Shanghai by German physician Erich Boron, has a history of 120 years, moving to Wuhan in 1955.
。
.
1月27日，由门诊办公室发出的紧急公告，可能是武汉同济医院历史上第一次——只开发热门诊，其他门诊全部暂停。
On January 27, an emergency bulletin issued by the outpatient department's office, probably for the first time in the history of Wuhan Tongji Hospital, opened only a hot clinic and all other outpatient clinics were suspended.
。
.
经济观察网记者有幸采访到奋战在抗疫第一线发热门诊的武汉同济医院心血管内科医生赵金召。
WAN reporter was privileged to interview Zhao Jin-chuang, a cardiovascular physician at Wuhan Tongji Hospital who fought in the front-line fever clinic against the epidemic.
。
.
自从大年初一与家人一起吃过午饭之后，武汉同济医院心血管内科医生赵金召医生就再没有回过家。
Since the New Year's Day lunch with his family, Wuhan Tongji Hospital Cardiovascular Physician Dr. Zhao Jin-chuang has never been home again.
奋战在抗疫第一线发热门诊的他，现在由医院统一安排酒店住宿，每天要接诊200至300病人（其中大部分都是新冠肺炎患者），他已有部分同事感染了新冠病毒。
Battle in the first-line anti-epidemic fever clinic, he is now a unified hospital accommodation arrangement, 200 to 300 patients per day (most of them are new crown pneumonia patients), he has some colleagues infected with the new crown virus.
。
.
当下疫情形势严峻，赵金召医生每天工作量极大，武汉同济医院每8小时一班，上班时间全部二级防护。
At present, the situation is serious, Dr. Zhao Jinqiao daily workload, Wuhan Tongji Hospital every eight hours, all secondary protection during working hours.
。
.
以下是经济观察网记者与赵金召医生对话实录：。
The following is a dialogue between Economic Watch journalists and Dr. Zhao Jinchuan.
经济观察网：赵医生您被隔离居住没有？您多久没有见到家人？您主动和家人隔离吗？。
Economic Observation Network: Have you been living in isolation, Dr. Zhao? How long have you not seen your family? Are you actively separated from your family?
赵金召医生：我是主动隔离的，大年初一中午一起吃过饭，后面就没见面了。
Dr. Zhao Jincheng: I am actively isolated, the New Year's Day lunch together, the back did not meet.
因为家里有老人小孩，为了安全，自己工作之余就住在医院安排的酒店里。
Because the family has old people and children, in order to be safe, their own work after living in hospital arranged hotel.
我会主动联系他们，主要通过视频的方式。
I'll get in touch with them, mainly via video.
。
.
经济观察网：您是什么科室的？武汉同济医院现在是不是只看肺炎发热门诊，其他门诊全部暂停？。
Economic Observation Network: What section are you? Wuhan Tongji Hospital is not only to see the pneumonia fever clinic, all the other clinics suspended?
赵金召医生：我是心血管内科的医生，目前武汉同济医院只有发热门诊和急诊，普通门诊全部停诊。
Dr. Zhao Jinchang: I am a doctor of cardiovascular medicine. Wuhan Tongji Hospital only has fever clinic and emergency department.
。
.
赵金召通过微信传来一份医院的通知，全文如下：。
Zhao Jin-chuang sent a notice of the hospital by micromail, as follows:
“根据国务院办公厅关于延长春节假期的通知精神和目前新型冠状病毒肺炎防控的需要，华中科大同济医院初发热门诊照常接诊外，其他门诊全部暂停，开诊时间另行通知。
"In accordance with the notice issued by the Cabinet Office of the State Council on the extension of the Spring Festival and the need for prevention and control of the new coronavirus pneumonia, all clinics have been suspended until further notice, except for the opening of the primary fever clinic at Tongji Hospital in Central China.
”落款为华中科大同济医院门诊办公室，时间是1月27日。
The appointment came on January 27 at the out-patient office of Tongji Hospital, Central China University.
。
.
经济观察网：说心里话，您自己心里紧张吗？恐惧吗？您的同事里有没有被感染的？。
Economic Watch: Speaking from the heart, are you nervous? Are you afraid? Are your colleagues infected?
赵金召医生：紧张， 不恐惧，有同事被感染。
Dr. Zhao Jincheng: Nervousness, no fear, colleagues are infected.
主要还是担心自己把病毒带回去传染给家人，家里有老人和小孩。
The main concern is to bring the virus back to their families, there are old people and children.
。
.
经济观察网：能否描述一下您的工作状态？是否每天都穿着防护服上班？是否汗如雨下？防护服是一次性的吗？一天需要更换几套防护服？医院目前防护服供应是否充足？。
Economic Observation Network: Can you describe your working status? Do you wear protective clothing to work every day? Is it raining? Are protective clothing disposable? How many suits do you need to change every day? Is the hospital's current supply of protective clothing adequate?
赵金召医生：我们是每八小时一班。
Dr. Zhao Jincheng: We leave every eight hours.
上班时间全部是二级防护——防护服、口罩、眼罩加面罩。
All working hours are secondary protective clothing, masks, eye masks and face masks.
穿防护服没有汗如雨下，里面穿单衣即可。
Wear protective clothing without sweat, can wear single clothes inside.
防护服是一次性的，根据需要，期间如果吃饭的话需要更换一次。
The protective clothing is one-time, according to the need, during the meal if the need for a change.
防护服够用，但不充足。
Protective clothing is sufficient, but not sufficient.
。
.
经济观察网：赵医生，你的家人是否非常担心你？在你工作期间因为隔离居住，是否每天同你联络以确定你的健康？。
Economic Observation Network: Dr. Zhao, do your family worry about you very much? Do you contact you every day to make sure you are healthy because you live in isolation during your work?
赵金召医生：家人担心，但能理解。
Dr. Zhao Jincheng: Family members are worried, but they understand.
知道我的责任和做这件事的意义。
Know my responsibility and what it means to do it.
会在我工作之余联系我。
I'll get in touch with you after work.
。
.
经济观察网：这次在武汉爆发的新冠病毒，是否您职业生涯中最惊险的一次？您现在每天需要照看多少病人？病人的病情如何？您所需要的药物和物资是否有短缺的情况？。
Economic Watch: Is this the most dangerous outbreak of the new crown virus in Wuhan? How many patients do you need to look after every day? What is the patient's condition? Are there any shortages of the drugs and materials you need?
赵金召医生：是我职业生涯中最惊险的。
Dr. Zhao Jincheng: It was the scariest thing in my career.
我主要在门诊。
I'm mainly out-patient.
门诊留观（指留院观察）病人大约在40人，另外每天大约有二百到三百的就诊病人。
The number of outpatient visits is about 40, and there are about 200 to 300 patients per day.
留观病人大多较重，不适合在家隔离，部分需要呼吸机辅助呼吸，每天能遇到死亡情况。
Most of the patients were heavy, not suitable for isolation at home, some need ventilator-assisted breathing, daily death can be encountered.
现在主要是医务人员人手不足。
It is mainly medical personnel who are understaffed.
医院的物资较前几天已经明显改善。
Hospital supplies have improved markedly compared to the previous days.
。
.
经济观察网：你们现在的工作强度如何？是否能够在承受范围之内？华中科大同济医院是否已经全部动员参与武汉新冠肺炎疫情的战斗中来？你们实行轮流上发热门诊吗？。
Economic Observation Network: What is the intensity of your work? Can you afford it? Has Tongji Hospital of CUHK been fully mobilized in the fight against the New Crown Pneumonia epidemic in Wuhan? Do you have a rotating fever clinic?
赵金召医生：医院早已满负荷运转，全员动员，轮流上岗，但以年轻医生为主，工作三年左右的医生占多数。
Dr. Zhao Jincheng: The hospital has been running at full capacity, mobilizing all staff, rotating on duty, but the majority of doctors working for about three years are young doctors.
。
.
经济观察网：一线疫情的抗争中，有没有什么让你特别感动或者特别想抱怨的事情？。
Economic Watch: Is there anything particularly moving or complaining about the first-line epidemic?
赵金召医生：四面八方的支援最让人感动，还有很多无名人士的捐献很让人感动，以及朋友的支持和家人的支持都让人感动。
Dr. Zhao Jincheng: The support from all sides was most moving. There were also many unnamed people whose contributions were very moving, as well as the support from friends and family.
某些机构的不作为和不专业让人抱怨，病人及家属的病痛以及不理解让人很无奈。
The inaction and lack of professionalism of some institutions is a source of complaint, and the illness and lack of understanding of patients and their families is overwhelming.
还有就是伤医事件不能容忍。
There is also the intolerance of injuries.
。
.
就在采访赵金召医生的1月30日，武汉市第四医院出现一起因岳父感染病毒性肺炎去世，家属殴打医生被刑拘的事件。
In an interview with Dr. Zhao Jincheng on January 30, Wuhan Fourth Hospital, a father-in-law died of viral pneumonia, the family beat the doctor was detained.
。
.
由于疫情严峻，战斗在一线门诊的赵金召医生非常繁忙，接受采访的时间很有限。
Due to the severe outbreak, the battle in the front-line clinic Dr. Zhao Jincheng very busy, the interview time is very limited.
。
.
武汉同济医院是本次新冠肺炎病毒的重点收治医院，基本上来的都是肺炎病人，网络上广泛流传出一篇武汉同济医院周宁医生疑似感染新冠肺炎后紧急自我隔离后自愈的文章，周宁医生正是因为给病人做手术过程中被感染。
Wuhan Tongji Hospital is the focus of the new crown pneumonia virus admission hospital, are basically all pneumonia patients, the network widely spread of a Wuhan Tongji Hospital, Dr. Zhou Ning suspected to be infected with pneumonia after emergency self-isolation after the self-healing, Dr. Zhou Ning is precisely because the patient was infected during surgery.
。
.
正是有了无数像赵金召医生这样奋战在疫情一线的白衣战士，武汉新型肺炎才有了被抑制的可能。
It is because of the innumerable white warriors such as Zhao Jin-cheng who fought on the front line of the epidemic that the new pneumonia in Wuhan could be suppressed.
。
.
在武汉同济医院的官网上，最新的一篇报道是1月28日的《让党旗飘扬在同济医院疫情防控的第一线》，里面有句话令人印象深刻：。
On the website of Wuhan Tongji Hospital, the latest report is "Let the Party Flag on the Front Line of Prevention and Control of Tongji Hospital" on January 28.
“不计报酬，无论生死，防疫一线我们上！”临时党支部书记门诊办公室主任李刚说，这是大家共同的心声。
"Ignore pay, whether life or death, epidemic prevention on our!" Temporary Party branch secretary out-patient office director Li Gang said, this is the common aspiration of all.
。
.
祝他们平安归来，无数像赵金召这样奋战门诊一线的医生。
Wish them safe return, countless doctors such as Zhao Jin-chuang fighting in front of the clinic.
。
.
