从事新闻行业超过12年，专注于时政、公司新闻报道，擅长采访、调查、取证和突破。
More than 12 years of journalism, specializing in current affairs, corporate journalism, good at interviewing, investigation, evidence gathering and breakthrough.
2006年起在经济观察报华东新闻中心（上海）工作，2008年派驻重庆，负责西南地区新闻报道。
Since 2006, he has worked in the East China Information Center (Shanghai) of the Economic Observer, and in 2008 he has been posted in Chongqing to cover the Southwest China News.
常驻重庆。
Resident in Chongqing.
